      "id": "PopularPost252803",
      "post_content": "Even with the both options on 1 card, neither side seems particularly useful. Usually land destruction is only good if the deck is devoted to it, and just a one-shot opponent's choice discard is not that useful at any stage in the game. I guess I'm missing something here.",
